501
00:37:35,247 --> 00:37:36,887
I am Lai Ji, the Prefectural Governor
of Tingzhou.

502
00:37:37,687 --> 00:37:39,847
Are you the general from
the Fuyan Governor's Mansion?

503
00:37:40,580 --> 00:37:43,072
[General of Fuyan, Ashina Duzhi]

504
00:37:43,072 --> 00:37:46,162
[Deputy General of Ashina Duzhi]

505
00:37:46,247 --> 00:37:50,567
In the past, our Tingzhou and Chumukun tribe
had no grudges and recent days have brought no feuds.

506
00:37:51,367 --> 00:37:52,807
You are leading troops to attack,

507
00:37:52,807 --> 00:37:55,767
and you are even planning to slaughter
all the people in our city to the last man,

508
00:37:55,767 --> 00:37:57,647
I don't know what the justification for this?

509
00:37:58,967 --> 00:38:01,487
You Tang people are despicable and shameless,

510
00:38:02,167 --> 00:38:06,787
Our Khan and his officers
kindly helped you to quell the rebellion,

511
00:38:06,787 --> 00:38:09,407
but Chief Administrator Su Haizheng,

512
00:38:09,407 --> 00:38:12,767
took them to the Tang camp and had them killed.

513
00:38:16,487 --> 00:38:20,567
Naturally,
such deep hatred and blood feud fall upon you.

514
00:38:21,247 --> 00:38:25,727
Today,
I will not stop until all of you are dead.

515
00:38:25,727 --> 00:38:30,487
How can we calm the Khan's
and the soldiers' resentment?

516
00:38:54,247 --> 00:38:55,488
My lord.

517
00:38:56,967 --> 00:38:58,272
What on earth has happened?

518
00:38:59,287 --> 00:39:01,347
The northerners have launched a massive invasion
and surrounded Tingzhou.

519
00:39:01,347 --> 00:39:02,847
The Prefectural Governor of Tingzhou, Lai Ji,
has died in battle.

520
00:39:03,847 --> 00:39:04,867
How many people have come?

521
00:39:04,867 --> 00:39:06,007
At least five thousand cavalry.

522
00:39:07,127 --> 00:39:09,467
Sir, the Prefectural Governor
of Tingzhou, Lai Ji,

523
00:39:09,467 --> 00:39:11,507
