from attacking the city.

524
00:39:11,507 --> 00:39:13,807
But the Northern men not only did not retreat.

525
00:39:13,807 --> 00:39:16,127
On the contrary,
they tightly besieged Tingzhou.

526
00:39:16,127 --> 00:39:18,087
Please, sir, quickly save Tingzhou.

527
00:39:25,407 --> 00:39:27,487
These Northerners are so ruthless
in their attack

528
00:39:28,167 --> 00:39:29,447
They obviously want revenge

529
00:39:30,927 --> 00:39:32,687
Father killed Khan Xingxiwang

530
00:39:33,567 --> 00:39:35,527
If this leads to the fall of Tingzhou

531
00:39:36,087 --> 00:39:37,087
or even a massacred city

532
00:39:38,487 --> 00:39:40,327
How can this matter be hidden
from the imperial court?

533
00:39:41,647 --> 00:39:43,047
Not to mention, those people from the north may

534
00:39:43,047 --> 00:39:44,527
