543
00:40:18,127 --> 00:40:21,727
I am willing to go to Tingzhou
to relieve the distress there.

544
00:40:37,167 --> 00:40:39,687
Why don't you agree?

545
00:40:40,767 --> 00:40:44,587
Chief Administrator Su focuses on killing
to establish his authority,

546
00:40:44,587 --> 00:40:47,456
